    {
      "say": "Ikazuchi? Inazuma? Why are you here?",
      "actor": 301090,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 301120,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "options": [
        {
          "content": "Happily accept their offer",
          "flag": 1
        }
      ],
      "say": "You've been working the whole day, and we thought you would like some refreshments. Care for a drink?",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "paintingFadeOut": {
        "time": 0.5,
        "side": 1
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Thank you, Inazuma!",
      "actor": 301090,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Hey, Commander, Akatsuki hasn't been causing any trouble, has she? We were a bit concerned, so we came to check in on you!",
      "actor": 301110,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "I've heard she got lost on the first day she was to serve as the secretary.",
      "actor": 301120,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 301090,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "Ugh...",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.15,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "And the other day when we were having tea, didn't she run off somewhere, leaving a note saying she'd gone looking for Hibiki?",
      "actor": 301110,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 301090,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "P-please, don't talk about that...!",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.1,
          "number": 3,
          "delay": 0,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Soon after, we received that photograph of Akatsuki and two polar bears in front of a tent. For being bears, they looked rather friendly.",
      "actor": 301120,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "I see! So that is what someone having \"no sense of direction\" means!",
      "actor": 301110,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Oh, yeah! Remember that one time when we were training, and Akatsuki went-",
      "actor": 301110,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "I think we should take our leave, Ikazuchi.",
      "actor": 301120,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Huh? But I was just getting-",
      "actor": 301110,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Our task here is done, so I believe we should head back. We wouldn't want to get in the way of their work, would we?",
      "actor": 301120,
      "side": 0,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "I see! Alright then, we're leaving now! See you two later!",
      "actor": 301110,
      "side": 1,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Before Ikazuchi could finish her story, she and Inazuma left the room.",
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "say": "Thank goodness they left...",
      "actor": 301090,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 301090,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "A-ahem! So, now you know much more about me. My inept side in particular. You must be very disappointed...",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 0,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.4,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0.4,
          "x": 22.5
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 301090,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "say": "I swear upon my title as a ninja that I will never get lost and never be afraid of the dark again! I shall overcome my weaknesses!",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "action": [
        {
          "y": 45,
          "type": "shake",
          "dur": 0.2,
          "number": 2,
          "delay": 0.5,
          "x": 0
        }
      ],
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "actor": 301090,
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "nameColor": "#a9f548",
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "speed",
          "active": true
        }
      ],
      "say": "Hiyah! Hooah! I'm feeling rather fired up! I'm ready to take on any task you have in store for me!",
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "painting": {
        "alpha": 0.3,
        "time": 1
      },
      "bgName": "bg_story_task"
    },
    {
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "speed",
          "active": false
        }
      ],
      "side": 2,
      "dir": 1,
      "typewriter": {
        "speed": 0.05,
        "speedUp": 0.01
      },
      "say": "Just like that, Akatsuki took her feelings of humility and turned them into determination.",
      "blackBg": true,
